Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,用部費再買個新的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這個月的部費  買完新枕頭就用光了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這枕頭原來真是用部費買的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不願意讓你拿我的甜心代用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這倆男生真是令人傷腦筋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,罪魁禍首…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我捏我捏…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.04,Comment,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐好狠毒!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有新的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但隔壁的儲藏室裡好像有個老的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁那是我們社團的儲藏室嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我入部的時候  就已經基本不使用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,夢子老師或許不知道拿哪一把鑰匙開門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那就問問小山老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,…喂  你們幹什麼呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這門真是不太好開…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…就這點程度  根本不算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,分明喘得這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,進去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,空間大概是活動室的一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,到處都是灰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,窗戶也不方便打開…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  日光燈也打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還是趁早趕緊找到它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,畫得真好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  好好找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這漫畫真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還是我小學時候讀過的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了  找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們正在休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就拜託你們關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得好緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看到沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你這副得意的表情是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這根本不算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,先別提這個  宇佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是和內卷同處一室…你也可千萬別因此失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}身不由己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,失控?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀…門一關就變熱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還是得通通風才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,…咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,卡得緊也不至於…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,居然這麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是是  是我小看你了  對不起  行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不該說你孱弱無力  骨瘦如柴  面色蒼白!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不…你沒說得這麼嚴重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  既然要道歉  就得更加有誠意才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,對…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  這箱子上寫著「石膏像」三個字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊  宇佐美同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  快來開門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,比一開始卡得更緊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,應該得怪你當時錘了一下門吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?  又成我的錯了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我臉上沾了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好近!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呼…呼出的氣息…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,輕叩著我的臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是可蕾特同學的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐他們回去了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她把老師叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學  聽得見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這扇門打不開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天色這麼晚了  我也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  手機呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沒戲  在包裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多要到放學時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷…如  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒有人注意到我們  該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,既然門打不開  也只得維持現狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的情況就是在這裡住一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(686.997,572.644)\frz248.5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs60\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\pos(691.497,611.644)\frz250.7}…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦  如果繼續變冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,別突然這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,才不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?  很暖和吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你從剛才開始就在說些什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,天已經黑透了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼蹲在角落裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  怎麼可能沒感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在慌死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…在這又小又黑的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,直到明早  都得二人…獨處…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,會起灰的  別打滾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學你沒事吧  剛才就怪怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,當然有事!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們倆得在這裡過一晚哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都開始胡思亂想那種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,部長說的那句話還怎麼反駁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別慌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,內…內卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  我可是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就給你看看我家甜心的厲害之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,摁下這個按鈕  眼睛就會發光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  真亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這還是我第一次覺得內卷你的手辦厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣做的話  或許會讓夜值巡邏的老師注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,確實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是又得好好巡邏才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊  夢子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  果然還是太黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那道光是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒人在才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,記得是這間來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才聽到什麼聲音了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你也聽到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是妖怪之類的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是以前部員的紀念照吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  來看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?  是照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  窗戶這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,像不像是一張臉?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說過讓你別嚇唬我了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再這樣我就把這個給折斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,比妖怪還可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你還來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嚇唬你啦  你看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這裡應該是這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是門吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,從位置上看  另一邊就是活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  你把那邊的箱子移開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害  原來這裡相連在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好可蕾特同學沒有把門鎖上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果就那樣待了一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道他們以後會怎麼捉弄我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,捉弄什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了石膏像了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,算了  說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我來搬石膏像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽打了好多通電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老師  您為何會在這種地方睡覺呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,無論是現在還是以前都會有人對石膏像塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz278\pos(275.997,206.644)}賢弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz262\pos(922.497,290.644)}大哥喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\b0\frz334\pos(267.997,373.811)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\frz336.9\pos(865.997,442.311)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和短髮波波頭合起來就是…波啵午安!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧  很有趣吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  這本漫畫也好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一本?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  這本我也看過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這本很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,女主角有超能力的那一部對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,必殺技非常帥氣  像這樣…啪啪噼里啪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這間隱藏房間真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,既可以盡情看漫畫又能夠放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎你隨時過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你們看起來聊得很高興的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做功課  所以可以請你們安靜一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  功課在家裡做不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們安靜一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  太安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,你到底想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我不就不知道你們在做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?  那當然是在看漫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太安靜的話總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喵喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有什麼夾在漫畫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,寶物的所在之處?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,給未來的美術部員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}俺有一寶貝疙瘩  就藏在咱校園裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,吾有秘寶  藏於黌門之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}看你們能解開謎題  去挖出寶貝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,望爾等窺破機關以繼承秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(945,990)}希望俺這寶貝能找個好人家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,若蒙菩薩心腸者得之  善哉善哉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害  是尋寶遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要玩玩看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我要玩  我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來剛好宇佐美同學就自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也能夠方便她集中精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們趕快開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,到了休息時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在剛好是休息時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,暗號1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,「離開活動室並前往紳士的小屋」上面這麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,紳士的小屋是指哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是腦筋急轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,順帶一提暗號2是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,「前往從紳士的小屋的窗戶看得見的這個地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我覺得至少是有窗戶的房間才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  是指男廁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,的確很「紳士」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這裡就麻煩內卷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因為身為淑女的我們是不能進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  淑女?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是了個是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是了個是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,從窗戶看得見的這的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一封奇怪的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒什麼特別的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你看她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(832.5,990)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1027.5,990)}拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣子想出來也不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候就是普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方  這個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(994.5,990)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是「這」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1140,990)}コ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  確實是這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺變得有趣起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學  下個提示是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,暗號3 「找出字母」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?  就這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,問題來了  登登
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡來看的話?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是U
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你真行  伊萬莉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我腦筋急轉彎淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個  暗號4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,「從找到的字母的末端開始  前進?步」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,「?步」?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,U的末端是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,步數是從1853到1890的向日葵的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道答案是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下  還不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,給一個提示  給一個提示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她很享受謎題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,提示  這是關於梵高的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(780,990)}Gogh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是什麼來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.08,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48}註：日語中「梵高」和「五步」的發音相似
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,1步  2步  3步  4步  5步!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?  宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉不是美術部員也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不對嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…內卷你來告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,梵高是1853出生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,1890過世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他是荷蘭的畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,畫家?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:19:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說暗號4的答案是梵高畫過的向日葵的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有1幅燒毀了  但是一共有7幅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是7步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密寶物一定就在這下面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  無論怎麼努力  這裡也不像是能挖的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看來沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼能挖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1065,990)}岡格尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,出現吧  永恆之槍!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:34.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48}註：Gungnir  岡格尼爾  北歐神話中主神奧丁所使用的武器  是矮人族用世界之樹的樹枝打造而成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好短!  永恆之槍好短!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  憑我的魔力這就是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就只有前端而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但這是永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有寫古文字嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯  畢竟是永恆之槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便丟也能挖?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,行了別鬧了  好了別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,體力勞動就交給就交給內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我來嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好像挖到什麼堅硬的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆之槍也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那我們就來進行開封儀式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,無論有什麼  都由我們三等分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我不是美術部員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是我們三人找到的  這是當然的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們重要的冒險證明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,色情…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要找什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,死零之書對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,各位也有在勤奮作畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.48,0:23:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀?  部長呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原來在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:24:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來…那邊的房間有很多書對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.10,0:24:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讓我幫忙找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  這個美術部大有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,魔導書和再次的散步  敬請期待
